Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in excelsis Deo. Praise to thee, O Lord. Amen. Today we have a shocking subject. Unpopular
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in current world. Very unpopular politically. The name of the subject is truth. So let's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,see. We have the slides set up. And how many people here are new? Okay. All right. So in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that case, we'll recapitulate some of the beginning slides as usual. So we can set the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,context. We always start with the map of consciousness. As you know, we evolved a relative scale from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.40,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,one to a thousand. And it was possible then to calibrate everything that existed now or
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:02:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,ever on a calibratable scale. What the scale differentiates is essence rather than
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,scale. And that's the difference. And that's the difference between essence and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.81,0:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,appearance. This is sort of a difficult concept. I noticed some people who have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,attended lectures who don't get it. What a thing looks like and what it is are
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,often different. So we'll do slide 111 and then we'll go back to the map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because what people don't get conceptually I think they can get
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.63,0:02:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,visually. Don't tell me how wonderful somebody who calibrates at 120 is. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you. So when we calibrate we're getting what is the essence and this is the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,appearance and to differentiate the two happens automatically in the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,conscious level about 600. The opening of the third eye of the Buddhic body it's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,called esoterically. From that point on a person's picks up essence but until
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,below that it's very easy to fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,With illusion. Okay I just wanted to do 111 because it's such a cute slide. It's a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,real find. So we go back to the slides the way they're supposed to be. Anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,what we discovered is that people who are integrous will go weak in response
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is negative and strong in response to that which is positive. This
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very fast response.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.49,0:03:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the acupuncture system we tend to get that we need to do three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,One is we need to balance ourselves and the other is we need to do the exact
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,same thing we need to do a couple of things and the acupuncture system
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,quickly rebalances rebalances you. So you look at something horrific you go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,weak for a second. However the body quickly corrects itself. So the response
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that we use the strength of the muscle is a very fast response and a lot of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to quick touch her, because if you wait long enough, you lose the reflex.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's very, very quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you can merely hold it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can say what I'm holding in mind calibrates over 200, 250, 300, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to tell her what I'm holding in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That negates the suspicion that it's a suggestion or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just an innate response, and we've given that its origin is in early emergence of animal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that the most primitive animal forms have some way to detect sources of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we're calibrating are levels of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And if an amoeba didn't know that that was negative or evil, he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't have any amoebas that are stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all the dumb ones kill themselves off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.18,0:05:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only eat arsenic so many times, and then there won't be any more amoeba around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, it was a means of protoplasm getting advanced information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say consciousness samples that which it witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and differentiates that which is pro-life from that which is anti-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, people below 200 cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They cannot do this because they are aligned not with life, but with that which is anti-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The lie, non-integrity, scheming, dishonesty, rape, pillage, murder, killing, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So only people who calibrate high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And the higher the people calibrate, the more accurate they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.04,0:06:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Some recent research came across my desk that was quite interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood of error goes down as your own level of consciousness goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough chit-chat on all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the map is finished worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's used in a great variety of ways and about to be used even in some more significant ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives us the level of truth of an integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It tells us what the essence, and that's enough about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrated skill of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.43,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, these are the circle slides, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, those that calibrate the highest have to do with divinity, which are infinite, infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,These are all infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.31,0:07:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then they come down to the worldly realm, a thousand, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the levels of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you can see that we have a means of confirming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All the aspects of divinity, all the aspects and qualities of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can see that the atheistic people would not be happy about this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And they aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And every time you read a critical blog or something, I'll say, the originator of this blog believes in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you negate the source of truth, then you don't have the gift of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.81,0:07:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the way to tell whether somebody is integrous, and this is going to be coming up soon, I'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,are you willing to swear allegiance to God and your fellow man and your country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.35,0:08:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the person refuses, they go in this pile over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use a weight that doesn't have any springs in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there was somebody who was so dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hasn't said, this is my own, my native land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Being unable to even love your fellow man puts you behind the eight ball when it comes to truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So in America, 50% of the people calibrate below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Worldwide, it's more like 85%.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.05,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:09:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So this realm, this is the energy as you go up the scale of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.03,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the energy in microwatts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.34,0:09:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So the power goes up the higher the level of truth and the higher the level of frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And as one would expect from this, the calibration of God's power is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll move to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,78% of the world's population, around 80% calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We just want to show how this is the mass of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used to call it the great unwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.08,0:09:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To my father, if you'd never read the great books of the Western world and didn't know Plato from Aristotle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you belong to the great unwashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the balance then, distribution of levels of consciousness of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:10:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, this is the great mass of humanity, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's counterbalanced by just this small little cap here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way this happens, the reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't self-destruct as a race,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is because the power of the few is greater than that of all the masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So the next slide shows that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So the people who do calibrate high are so enormously more powerful
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that they hold off the great masses who calibrate low, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fortunate for survival, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll go on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Percent of...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Every last time, the evolution of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a graph, which we'll have to correct
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because now it's going to show a hook over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.53,0:10:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it went down again a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.12,0:10:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,three or four points in the last few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we see that the evolution over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.85,0:11:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,these are archeologic ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we see how the energy field of life
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,rose progressively over great eons of archeologic time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,From the...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,From the most primitive protozoa on up to the higher levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it evolved as well as you would expect in the animal kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore you see bacteria, we use bacteria as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.98,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Protozoa, crustaceans, insects, arachnids, fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the friendly octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you get to the vipers, the Komodo dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They always wear shoes when you get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you come to the predatory mammals, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the lower levels, they live by the death of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we get to the level of 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And there you see a transition to the herbivores,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,people who are benign
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and live not at the cost of the life of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So the herbivores are the grazers,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they form the feedstuff for the more voracious ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.33,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get up to farmhorses and racehorses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what can you say about people who hate dogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really hard to handle a 245.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course a dog's wagging tail is 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now there's people that abuse dogs in the news, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting them to fight with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So family dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The family dog calibrates at 250.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So once a cat or a dog, or I suppose other pets,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.39,0:12:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,are around human beings, their consciousness evolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Their consciousness evolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So a family dog calibrates higher than a wild dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the monkeys, of course, we love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we have the gorillas and the chimps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we have these exceptional animals, Coco, the trained gorilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and remember the gorilla picking up the child that fell into the cage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was really quite something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we come to the capacity for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the cat's purr and the dog's wagging tail is actually love.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The kitty loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You love the kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And they actually love you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.07,0:13:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They love you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,An animal can love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safer with a loving kitty and a loving wagging tail dog
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,than you are with over 50% of the people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to give you a moment of thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.39,0:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safer with a cat and a dog than you are with 50% of the people on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.97,0:14:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want to avoid naivete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Naivete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Realizing that, you won't be taken advantage of and become a victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The great books of the Western world, as I've already mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,represent scholasticism, the best thinking from ancient Greece,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,down through time, through the period of the Enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one, I think, in this series is Freud.
