Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.38,0:24:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is more abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,More abstract. It's more than
