Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.02,0:25:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is a more
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.13,0:25:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,abstract notion
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.32,0:25:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,with sort of philosophic,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.97,0:25:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,metaphysical overtones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.52,0:25:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.05,0:25:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.51,0:25:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the first thing we notice
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.66,0:25:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,in the great books of the Western world,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.42,0:25:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mentioned Descartes,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.25,0:25:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,who pointed out the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,perception and essence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.88,0:25:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,between the lamb
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.21,0:25:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and the sheep and the wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.00,0:25:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He said,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.94,0:25:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Descartes,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.07,0:25:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the problem is the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.39,0:25:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,between res interna and res
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.36,0:25:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,externa, meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.45,0:25:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the world as you see it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.17,0:25:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,as compared to the world
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.56,0:25:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's a barrier there between.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.26,0:25:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the capacity to see what actually is,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.60,0:25:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is limited and relatively unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.08,0:25:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people go by opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.30,0:25:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Res interna, that is my idea of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.97,0:25:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the way I see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.21,0:25:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, that's the famous argument
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.36,0:26:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,referred to in Plato.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.01,0:26:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Protagoras says, well, the world I see is my reality
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.74,0:26:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world that you see is your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.79,0:26:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he made the incorrect assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.50,0:26:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, there is no ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.79,0:26:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have said,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.79,0:26:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,which proves that I am dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.79,0:26:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fact that people have different opinions
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.64,0:26:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean there's different realities.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.14,0:26:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just different perceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.64,0:26:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.64,0:26:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.14,0:26:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates' dictum is all that any spiritual student needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.97,0:26:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Socrates' dictum was that man chooses
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.23,0:26:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,only the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.02,0:26:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just that he doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.02,0:26:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,how to comprehend the difference between the real good
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.99,0:26:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the illusory good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.67,0:26:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But every man is choosing the good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.27,0:26:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you think it's good to blow you all up,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.66,0:26:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then that's his idea of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.51,0:27:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Good is killing all such people because you're all infidels.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.31,0:27:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be able to forgive would require, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.55,0:27:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a recognition of that inner reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.07,0:27:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that each person is seeking what
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.27,0:27:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,they believe to be the good and, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.77,0:27:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,capable of salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.27,0:27:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.64,0:27:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In today's world, however, popularity
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.48,0:27:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,reigns and the herd instinct, the media bias,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.53,0:27:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and, of course, the memes, which are the repeated phrases that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.53,0:27:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,are repeated often enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.57,0:27:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take a lie and repeat it often enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.64,0:27:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,people will believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.44,0:27:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,People will believe a lie if you just repeat it often enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.01,0:27:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, oh, no, I wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.88,0:27:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you will, under experimental conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.50,0:27:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,By the end of the experiment, I'll
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.97,0:27:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,have you convinced that your front is your back
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.49,0:28:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and your back is your front.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.03,0:28:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.24,0:28:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the world's great dictators
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.68,0:28:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,have depended on this, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.38,0:28:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Media bias.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the extraordinary popular
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.11,0:28:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Delusions and the Madness of Crowds
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.98,0:28:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,by Mackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.88,0:28:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was written, I don't know, in the late 1700s, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.41,0:28:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gives examples of how the whole world believes a certain thing
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and it turns out to be illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.06,0:28:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, he used the tulip craze in Holland.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.63,0:28:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this because you say, well, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.24,0:28:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, global warming is due to man,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.40,0:28:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,extraordinary popular delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.79,0:28:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody believes that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.57,0:28:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's man that causes global warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.07,0:28:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.36,0:29:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so everybody believes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.96,0:29:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a popular delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.11,0:29:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody believes it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.01,0:29:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's due to the slant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.83,0:29:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's due to ignoring the fact that these things are,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.61,0:29:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that the temperature of the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.24,0:29:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it reflects the magnetic activity
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.40,0:29:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on the surface of the sun for tens of thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.16,0:29:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And what man is doing is contributing contamination,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.64,0:29:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,contamination.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.77,0:29:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But contamination is not warming, global warming.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.68,0:29:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fly over the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.56,0:29:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you quickly leave the populated area.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.15,0:29:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And you then fly for hours and hours over nothingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.39,0:29:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,thousands and thousands of miles of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.41,0:29:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no people there creating pollution.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.02,0:29:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So pollution is caused by people,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.36,0:29:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and global warming is due to something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.78,0:29:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so that makes you a heretic, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.28,0:29:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Very people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.25,0:30:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Few people care to be a heretic and considered a madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.28,0:30:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because of political slant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.93,0:30:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So in our world, truth is overridden by political slant.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.01,0:30:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And as Bush said, money trumps peace, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.86,0:30:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Money trumps peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.54,0:30:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Politics and money, then, dominate our society.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.28,0:30:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the confusion of truth with these previous things
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.65,0:30:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is that it's confused with opinion and faith and belief
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.13,0:30:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,systems and data, which is often false.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.15,0:30:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondhand smoke is also another illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.32,0:30:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And the federal court actually threw it out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.91,0:30:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,as stupid junk science.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.49,0:30:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoking's bad for you, but secondhand smoke
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.69,0:30:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,has no bad effect whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.89,0:30:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway, that makes you a heretic, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.66,0:30:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,because the ordinary popular delusions has people convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.33,0:30:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And this has to do with the fact that we're not going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.98,0:31:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,able to get rid of the fact that these studies are well funded.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.74,0:31:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I want to get some money out of the government,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.99,0:31:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I just conjure up something.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.51,0:31:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The secondhand smoke causes schizophrenia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.16,0:31:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll get the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.55,0:31:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I put out a paper that secondhand smoke is not
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.01,0:31:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,related to schizophrenia, you won't get any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.11,0:31:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So political slant, then, influences science, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.53,0:31:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So political slant, then, influences science, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.53,0:31:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So political slant, then, influences science, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.83,0:31:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what we mean by falsified data.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.02,0:31:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Falsified data, I could give you better selections
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.69,0:31:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of falsified data, which the medical world doesn't even
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.65,0:31:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,know, and the world doesn't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.34,0:31:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll say, well, a certain treatment only
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.99,0:31:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,works 5% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.78,0:31:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.98,0:31:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or another treatment only works 50% of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.64,0:31:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.35,0:32:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What they fail to see is from that selected population, the 5%
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.39,0:32:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is 100% of that group.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.95,0:32:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know how to select in the group,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,the recovery rate is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.06,0:32:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If I tell people who are depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.09,0:32:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,stop eating sugar and sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.68,0:32:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,stop eating sugar and sweets,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,probably 40% will recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.79,0:32:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how many will recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.74,0:32:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take people that walk into the clinic,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.09,0:32:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they're depressed,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.25,0:32:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,over 30% of function hypoglycemia,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.56,0:32:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,35%, 40%.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.70,0:32:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so about 35% of people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.46,0:32:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,will recover from depression
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.18,0:32:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,if they stop eating sugar and sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.90,0:32:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So in that subgroup,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.72,0:32:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,your recovery rate is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.53,0:32:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't say sugar-free diets are worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.86,0:32:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try them in a large group of people,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.25,0:32:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll get a small recovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.84,0:32:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the population at large.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.58,0:32:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But amongst the select group,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.49,0:33:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,your recovery rate is 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.49,0:33:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So the clinician is one who can intuit
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.63,0:33:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and by lots of experience over many years,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.98,0:33:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of get which group
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.14,0:33:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.20,0:33:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Which this person falls into, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.53,0:33:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one he falls into.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.33,0:33:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I used to get appointments made by phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.33,0:33:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say stop eating sugar and sweets
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.09,0:33:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and take a lot of vitamin B3
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.77,0:33:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll see you in a week, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.02,0:33:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And about half the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.26,0:33:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time they walked into the office,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say, I don't know why I'm here, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.21,0:33:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anxiety attacks and depression
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.00,0:33:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are very often functional hypoglycemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.79,0:33:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The body puts out too much insulin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.33,0:33:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so you want to avoid things
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.88,0:33:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that create insulin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.66,0:33:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you switch from glucose and sucrose to fructose,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.59,0:33:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the hypoglycemia goes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.11,0:33:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fruit sugar does not stimulate an insulin response.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.72,0:33:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, it doesn't cost anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.61,0:33:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The cost to the taxpayer is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.51,0:34:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And the likelihood of success is extremely high
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.25,0:34:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know how to pick the subgroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.27,0:34:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm just pointing out the source,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.64,0:34:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the fallacies of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.88,0:34:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The data will say that, well, this is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.09,0:34:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It only cures 10%.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.76,0:34:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that 10%, the cure rate is 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.78,0:34:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an historic human deficiency,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.78,0:34:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the incapacity to tell truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.40,0:34:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We now corroborate truth by calibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.09,0:34:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So for the first time really in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.88,0:34:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,we have an objective means of verifying truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.96,0:34:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And as you can see from that previous diagram,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,truth is dependent on context,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.40,0:34:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and understanding of truth is level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.03,0:34:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To truly know a thing is actually to be aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.30,0:34:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To know a thing is to be aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.80,0:34:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.71,0:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So lots of people know about certain subjects,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.71,0:34:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,but to know it, you have to become it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.88,0:34:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to become it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.84,0:34:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,To know, you know about hermits,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but unless you're a hermit,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.23,0:34:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't know what it is to be a hermit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.25,0:35:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very hermity to be a hermit, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.55,0:35:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In our society, you have the impact of the media,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.82,0:35:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,which is enormous,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.98,0:35:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and caters to narcissism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.44,0:35:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And narcissism, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.96,0:35:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's projectionism.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.09,0:35:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's projected self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.09,0:35:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you've already salted the mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.09,0:35:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already decided on the outcome,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.09,0:35:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you go back and cite some incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.09,0:35:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This typifies our current society,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is almost 100% narcissistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.38,0:35:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.38,0:35:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.38,0:35:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.61,0:35:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Media are completely narcissistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.61,0:35:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is sold.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.80,0:35:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The Me Tube, the iTube, the YouTube.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.92,0:35:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.92,0:35:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.57,0:35:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.15,0:35:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,YouTube, there's only Me Tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.38,0:36:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So narcissism is self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.38,0:36:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And the bias that comes across is just constant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.42,0:36:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're aligned with truth and integrity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.42,0:36:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and logic,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.42,0:36:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just very difficult listening to the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.42,0:36:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because almost every single political statement
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.42,0:36:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is distorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.42,0:36:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost every political statement leaves out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.42,0:36:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,a key word that would totally change your picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.42,0:36:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why they purposely leave that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.42,0:36:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.44,0:36:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So a projected self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.82,0:36:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say, why is everybody so interested
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.82,0:36:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that the whole world should agree with them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.21,0:36:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and that the world should go along with what they think?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.21,0:36:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.21,0:36:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what's the gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.25,0:36:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.46,0:36:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the gain?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.46,0:36:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.46,0:36:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It feeds on itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.46,0:36:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Narcissism feeds on itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.46,0:36:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If everybody agrees with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.75,0:36:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,now your sense of importance goes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.75,0:37:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's your sense of importance
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.75,0:37:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that dominate the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.75,0:37:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It creates a sense of self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.75,0:37:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the animal world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.75,0:37:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,dominate brings about survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.75,0:37:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In the animal world,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.88,0:37:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't necessarily lead to survival at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.88,0:37:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It very often leads to its opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.88,0:37:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Narcissism distorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.88,0:37:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Projected self-interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.48,0:37:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And all you get out of it is a sense of grandiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.51,0:37:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A sense of grandiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.09,0:37:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If everybody agrees with my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.09,0:37:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm a great and happy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.09,0:37:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And if they don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.09,0:37:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then I'm a miserable failure, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.09,0:37:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's the way the ego works.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.09,0:37:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So people then want to propagate
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.09,0:37:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,their own belief systems on others
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.09,0:37:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because they get an immediate payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.15,0:37:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody has to think the way they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.15,0:37:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,All mentation, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.57,0:37:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,reflects a limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.80,0:37:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is really unable, by its design,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.80,0:38:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to be able to discern truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.40,0:38:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain is like a hardware of the computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the mentation is like the software.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.40,0:38:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All mentation reflects limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.76,0:38:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So whatever you think is already a limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.94,0:38:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.98,0:38:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.50,0:38:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that transcends the limitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.53,0:38:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to know truth is already limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.53,0:38:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see from the diagram on brain physiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.57,0:38:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that brain function itself
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.69,0:38:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,limits the capacity to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.69,0:38:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and comprehend reality and truth
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.69,0:38:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,amongst people that are below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.94,0:38:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Half the population, therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.94,0:38:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is frankly, intrinsically,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.94,0:38:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of brain physiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.23,0:39:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,unable to comprehend abstract truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.23,0:39:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,anything 200 and up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.23,0:39:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that has to do with context.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.65,0:39:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the errors that you see
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.84,0:39:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,day after day after day on the television
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.84,0:39:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with this limitation of brain function,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.15,0:39:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of calibration levels below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.38,0:39:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who have their own heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.51,0:39:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and political parties and belief systems
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.51,0:39:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and their own cheering sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.51,0:39:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They have their own block sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.05,0:39:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst block site I know of calibrates at 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.55,0:39:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it sort of specializes in hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.55,0:39:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Specializes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.57,0:39:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't even tell you the name,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.73,0:39:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's so awful,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.73,0:39:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to even glance at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.76,0:39:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Specializing in hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.90,0:39:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Specializing in hatred, you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.90,0:39:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what could people get out of putting
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.90,0:39:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all that hateful stuff on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.90,0:39:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it lies, all of it hateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.90,0:39:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it derogatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.90,0:40:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,all of it fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.90,0:40:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What could a person get out of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.90,0:40:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They get being who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.86,0:40:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The naivete, the human mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.94,0:40:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I was saying, what's their motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.94,0:40:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Folks, they don't have any motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.46,0:40:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the few people on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.32,0:40:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.32,0:40:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have any motive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.28,0:40:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.61,0:40:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a guy named, what was his name, KOS,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.61,0:40:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that killed all the people in some university
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.61,0:40:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and had a hate video that he put on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.84,0:40:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and he just ranted hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.88,0:40:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he the Virginia Tech killer or somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.48,0:40:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lowest I've ever calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.26,0:40:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.07,0:40:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.63,0:40:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, well, he must have had a troubled childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.82,0:41:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His mother must have had a troubled childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.00,0:41:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the motive of a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.82,0:41:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the motive behind wickedness?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.82,0:41:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.98,0:41:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just being what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.98,0:41:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.23,0:41:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no bad childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.23,0:41:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that caused their resentment,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.23,0:41:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that caused maybe so-and-so,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.23,0:41:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and if we just get them a good therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.23,0:41:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As one of those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.44,0:41:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,what would I do with a therapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.44,0:41:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.78,0:41:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They deserve to die
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.57,0:41:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're saying there's something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.57,0:41:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So I will have to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.57,0:41:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.40,0:42:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.46,0:42:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Identity defines essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.46,0:42:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them the story about the frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.69,0:42:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The frog and something rides on his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.09,0:42:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who rides on his back?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.42,0:42:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.90,0:42:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the scorpion rides on the back of the frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.36,0:42:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.36,0:42:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.82,0:42:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, tell them that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.65,0:42:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.65,0:42:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.50,0:42:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.50,0:42:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.50,0:42:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.50,0:42:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a frog and a scorpion,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.50,0:42:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and the scorpion went across the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.50,0:42:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So he got on top of the back of the frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.50,0:42:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.69,0:42:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And as they're going across the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.69,0:42:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the scorpion, he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.75,0:42:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,now, you will not sting me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.75,0:42:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the scorpion says,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.75,0:42:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,no, I won't sting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.75,0:43:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't sting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.75,0:43:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're going across the pond,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.75,0:43:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.75,0:43:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the scorpion stings the frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.75,0:43:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, he's dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.75,0:43:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.75,0:43:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you said you wouldn't sting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.75,0:43:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, why'd you sting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.75,0:43:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.75,0:43:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's because that's what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.84,0:43:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.84,0:43:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what people don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.07,0:43:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I am a scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.61,0:43:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.61,0:43:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because that's what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.03,0:43:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.03,0:43:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in dealing with,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.36,0:43:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in dealing with people and political systems
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.36,0:43:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which wish to extinguish you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.36,0:43:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,extinguish you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.36,0:43:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody in here is an infidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.51,0:43:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.67,0:43:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You all deserve to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.80,0:43:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the proclamation
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.80,0:43:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of America's enemies right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.01,0:43:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.01,0:43:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.86,0:43:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.86,0:43:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what that energy does
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.65,0:44:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it sees the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.65,0:44:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it's anybody's fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.84,0:44:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,nor do I wish to blame anybody at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.03,0:44:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.03,0:44:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,sometimes spiritual alignment
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.26,0:44:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,leads to a naivete and a denial
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.26,0:44:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of a wimpism
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.98,0:44:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's supposed to be peace marches and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.98,0:44:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Best thing to do, folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.05,0:44:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,with a peace march
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.05,0:44:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is to blow them the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.96,0:44:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To call a spade a spade
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.96,0:44:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is not politically popular in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.28,0:44:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,where euphemisms are used to distort images
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.86,0:44:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and cover up the underlying reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.86,0:44:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.86,0:44:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll go to the next slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.36,0:45:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we believe to be truth
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.46,0:45:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is subject to programming
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.46,0:45:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and indoctrination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.46,0:45:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.61,0:45:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the dangers of today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.61,0:45:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is the indoctrination of the youth
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.61,0:45:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of other people,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.61,0:45:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,other cultures
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.61,0:45:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that are out to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.61,0:45:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.67,0:45:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Programming and indoctrination.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.67,0:45:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And today's,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.80,0:45:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this week's news
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.80,0:45:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is the Mickey Mouse cartoon
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.84,0:45:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,currently in Islam.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.84,0:45:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mickey Mouse
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.84,0:45:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.84,0:45:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,just shouted,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.84,0:45:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,shouted Haiti of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.84,0:45:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mickey Mouse became
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.84,0:45:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,liked by the children
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.84,0:45:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,over in those Islamic societies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.84,0:45:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the last edition
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.84,0:45:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a week ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.84,0:45:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the Israelis murdered Mickey Mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.84,0:45:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So the news media
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.84,0:45:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,all over now
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.84,0:45:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is how horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.84,0:45:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Americans and Israelis
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.84,0:45:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.84,0:45:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.84,0:45:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,they slaughtered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.84,0:45:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They murdered Mickey Mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.84,0:46:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was some little kid
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.28,0:46:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in another culture
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.28,0:46:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and watched Mickey Mouse
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.28,0:46:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,being slaughtered,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.28,0:46:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hate those people,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.28,0:46:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.46,0:46:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.46,0:46:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.46,0:46:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's inculcated hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.46,0:46:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,inculcated hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.46,0:46:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nazi propaganda minister Goebbels
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.46,0:46:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,was the world's best at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.46,0:46:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He compared Jews to worms
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.46,0:46:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and mice and rats
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.73,0:46:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.73,0:46:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And he did it visually.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.73,0:46:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So a picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.73,0:46:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you've already been programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.73,0:46:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to get
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.07,0:46:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,how fast your mind is programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.07,0:46:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you see that picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.07,0:46:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you just got programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.07,0:46:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, nobody's programming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.07,0:46:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already been programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.21,0:46:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.21,0:46:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.42,0:46:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is one image of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.42,0:46:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You just had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.42,0:46:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got imprinted
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.71,0:46:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with that image.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.71,0:46:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.71,0:46:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.90,0:46:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the chances of arriving
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.90,0:46:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,at a capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.90,0:46:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to discern truth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.90,0:46:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and stand for truth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.90,0:46:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and live a life of truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.90,0:46:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you see how slim it is
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.90,0:46:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in today's world
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.90,0:47:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,under the sheer media barrage.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.90,0:47:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So the human mind
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.98,0:47:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is subject to programming
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.98,0:47:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and constant indoctrination,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.98,0:47:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,constant indoctrination.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.98,0:47:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is different than,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.21,0:47:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,truth has to do with
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.21,0:47:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what does the thing mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.21,0:47:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can define a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.21,0:47:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you can give its linear definition,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.21,0:47:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but then,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.21,0:47:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.34,0:47:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So that brings us
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.34,0:47:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to the hermeneutics of abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.40,0:47:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermeneutics.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.40,0:47:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the science
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.40,0:47:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or philosophy of meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.40,0:47:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What does a thing mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.40,0:47:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermeneutics.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.40,0:47:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember I discussed
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.53,0:47:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the problematic hermeneutics
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.53,0:47:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of relativistic epistemology?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.53,0:47:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never gotten a blog
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.53,0:47:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,or an email
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.53,0:47:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,criticizing me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.38,0:47:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a one
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.38,0:47:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,has ever contested.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.38,0:47:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.26,0:47:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,then I get an answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.26,0:47:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.26,0:47:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what the answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.26,0:47:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.05,0:47:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,what the answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.05,0:47:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.05,0:47:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,what the answer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.05,0:47:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.05,0:47:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,then I get a nasty email.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.05,0:47:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.05,0:47:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,well,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.05,0:47:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find that out
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.05,0:48:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if you study the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.11,0:48:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,problematic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.11,0:48:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,hermeneutics
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.11,0:48:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of relativistic epistemology.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.11,0:48:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.11,0:48:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.30,0:48:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't criticize a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.30,0:48:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,until you understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.30,0:48:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't keep
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.30,0:48:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,bloggers from off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.30,0:48:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.76,0:48:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,what they do with themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.76,0:48:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,all evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.76,0:48:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.76,0:48:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.76,0:48:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a blogger is somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.76,0:48:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,who reads something
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.76,0:48:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't like
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.76,0:48:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and they just go,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.76,0:48:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,snort.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.86,0:48:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.86,0:48:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,if you,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.86,0:48:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you dumb AA,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.86,0:48:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,which immediately gets
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.82,0:48:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,picked on everybody's
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.82,0:48:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,blog site
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.48,0:48:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and quoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.48,0:48:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.48,0:48:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't criticize
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.73,0:48:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.73,0:48:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you can first
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.73,0:48:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,comprehend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.73,0:48:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.73,0:48:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,when people criticize
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.73,0:48:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,some things I've written,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.73,0:48:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.73,0:48:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,first read the book,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.73,0:48:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,then let me hear it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.03,0:48:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we use
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.03,0:48:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the RMI,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.03,0:48:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.03,0:48:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,do they read the book?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.03,0:48:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We always got to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.73,0:48:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All the people
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.73,0:48:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,who criticize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.28,0:48:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,over 2%
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.50,0:49:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,have read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.50,0:49:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 3%,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.88,0:49:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,5%,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.88,0:49:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,4%,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.88,0:49:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,3%,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.59,0:49:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,3%
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.59,0:49:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,have at least
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.17,0:49:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,tried to read the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.17,0:49:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard reading,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.17,0:49:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.17,0:49:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.17,0:49:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.80,0:49:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and we know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.80,0:49:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what the fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.80,0:49:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.17,0:49:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what the facts are,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.17,0:49:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and we know
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.17,0:49:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.17,0:49:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.17,0:49:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.17,0:49:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the implication?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.17,0:49:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.17,0:49:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,when you talk
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.17,0:49:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,about meaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.17,0:49:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,you're talking
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.17,0:49:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,about now levels
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.17,0:49:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.17,0:49:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.17,0:49:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.17,0:49:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.17,0:49:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,it means
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.17,0:49:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it's one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.30,0:49:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to this
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.30,0:49:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or that,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.30,0:49:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but what does it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.30,0:49:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,actually mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.13,0:49:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.13,0:49:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.69,0:49:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.69,0:49:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,for abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.69,0:49:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.82,0:49:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.82,0:49:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the people
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.82,0:49:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,do not have
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.82,0:49:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.82,0:49:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,for abstraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.98,0:49:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They are,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.98,0:49:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,deal only
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.98,0:49:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in the pedestrian,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.98,0:49:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,limited
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.98,0:49:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,idea
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.98,0:49:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.98,0:49:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,reductive
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.98,0:49:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,materialism.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.98,0:50:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.13,0:50:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.13,0:50:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,provable
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.13,0:50:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,within a very
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.13,0:50:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,limited
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.13,0:50:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,paradigm,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.13,0:50:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then it's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.13,0:50:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,fallacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.19,0:50:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.19,0:50:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that famous
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.19,0:50:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,guy that was
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.57,0:50:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,in the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.57,0:50:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Phoenix newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.57,0:50:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that's written
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.57,0:50:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,four or five
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.57,0:50:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,books claiming
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.57,0:50:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that Einstein
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.57,0:50:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.57,0:50:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And he keeps
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.57,0:50:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,writing more
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.57,0:50:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,books about
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.57,0:50:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein being
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.57,0:50:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a fraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.57,0:50:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What he doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.57,0:50:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,get is that
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.57,0:50:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,he doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.57,0:50:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,understand
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.09,0:50:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein's
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.09,0:50:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,work.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.09,0:50:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.32,0:50:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.32,0:50:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.32,0:50:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.32,0:50:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermeneutics
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.67,0:50:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of abstraction
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.67,0:50:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.67,0:50:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,context,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.67,0:50:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.67,0:50:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,context.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.67,0:50:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And to be
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.67,0:50:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,pedestrian
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.67,0:50:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,means to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.67,0:50:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,only see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.67,0:50:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the content,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.67,0:50:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.67,0:50:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the linear
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.76,0:50:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,concrete
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.76,0:50:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,content.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.76,0:50:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.76,0:50:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.76,0:50:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It can only
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.76,0:50:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,be viewed
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.90,0:50:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,from the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.90,0:50:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,level of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.90,0:50:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.90,0:50:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.90,0:50:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.90,0:50:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,like significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.11,0:51:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.11,0:51:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,significance
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.40,0:51:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.40,0:51:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.40,0:51:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,or for
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.57,0:51:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.57,0:51:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.63,0:51:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,a
