Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.96,0:52:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,live one day at a time, you know. Forgive and forget. Live one day at a time. Easy does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.51,0:52:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Live and let live. Paddle your own canoe. Instead of trying to paddle others. So
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.50,0:52:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this becomes a mental habit, a mental habit, and it influences probability,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.38,0:52:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,whereas mathematically the probability is of a different dimension. Once the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.76,0:52:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,attention set begins to set in, probability is that you're going to pick
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.07,0:52:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a peaceful solution more and more often. Also you will not be happy with the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.98,0:52:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,resentment. You may get over resentment, you may juice it for a little while, but
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.76,0:52:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,eventually you find that you don't like living with it. So instead of getting
