Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.21,0:53:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,should get even with you, or get that parking space, or whatever it is. Buy the
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.46,0:53:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,last copy of, what's the name of the book that's out now? Harry Potter. Get to the
