Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.40,0:53:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,influences our habitual choice, and we favor that which is more and more
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.59,0:53:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,peaceful and loving. So peacefulness and lovingness then give it to be habitual.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.78,0:53:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why people say what can I do for world peace and to solve the world's
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.23,0:53:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,problems, etc. And I would say to be as loving as possible towards all that
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.92,0:54:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,exists, and to walk over the little black beetle instead of squishing him. You're
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.88,0:54:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,already serving God in the world by saving his little life, because out of
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.84,0:54:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion you don't want to extinguish life unless you're actually forced to. So
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.59,0:54:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the influence of attention set is actually a
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.26,0:54:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,physiologic,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,neurologic phenomena so by consistently making certain choices your neurologic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.21,0:54:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,set your neurologic propensities the way the neurons are being to fire begin to
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.01,0:54:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,fire more and more favorably in a certain direction the more often you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.50,0:54:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,pick something negative the more likely it is you're going to pick the negative
